                      <footer><span>{{strengthLabel}} strength / {{manpowerUse}} manpower</span><button type="submit" {{#unless canEditAssignments}}disabled{{/unless}} title="Save regiment"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i></button>{{#if @root.isGM}}<button type="button" class="ds-danger" data-click-action="deleteTroop" data-settlement-id="{{@root.selected.id}}" data-troop-id="{{id}}" data-confirm="Delete this regiment?" title="Delete regiment"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash"></i></button>{{/if}}</footer>
                    </form>
                    {{#if missingCount}}<form class="ds-replenish-bar" data-action-form="queueReplenishment"><input type="hidden" name="settlementId" value="{{@root.selected.id}}"><input type="hidden" name="troopId" value="{{id}}"><span><i class="fa-solid fa-kit-medical"></i> {{missingCountDisplay}} casualties / {{replenishmentCostDisplay}} Crown each / no building or recruitment-capacity requirement</span><input type="number" name="targetCount" value="{{missingCount}}" min="1" max="{{missingCount}}"><button type="submit" {{#unless canReplenish}}disabled{{/unless}} title="Schedule month-end replenishment"><i class="fa-solid fa-rotate"></i></button></form>{{/if}}
                  </article>
                {{else}}<div class="ds-inline-empty">No regiments raised.</div>{{/each}}
              </div>
            </section>
          </section>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if (eq activeTab "chronicle")}}
          <section class="ds-pane ds-chronicle-layout">
            <form class="ds-panel" data-action-form="updateTurnNote"><input type="hidden" name="settlementId" value="{{selected.id}}"><div class="ds-panel-heading"><h2>Turn Note</h2><button type="submit" {{#unless selected.canWriteTurnNote}}disabled{{/unless}}><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i><span>Save</span></button></div><textarea name="turnNote" rows="8" {{#unless selected.canWriteTurnNote}}disabled{{/unless}}>{{selected.currentTurnNote.text}}</textarea><small>{{selected.currentTurnNote.updatedLabel}}</small></form>
            {{#if isGM}}<section class="ds-panel"><div class="ds-panel-heading"><h2>All Player Notes</h2></div>{{#each selected.allTurnNotes}}<article class="ds-log-entry"><h3>{{authorName}} <span>{{updatedLabel}}</span></h3><pre>{{text}}</pre></article>{{else}}<div class="ds-inline-empty">No player notes.</div>{{/each}}</section>{{/if}}
            <section class="ds-panel ds-chronicle-log"><div class="ds-panel-heading"><h2>Event Log</h2></div>{{#each selected.eventLog}}<article class="ds-log-entry"><h3>{{title}} <span>Month {{month}} / {{createdLabel}}</span></h3><pre>{{text}}</pre>{{#if gmNote}}<pre class="ds-gm-note">{{gmNote}}</pre>{{/if}}{{#if playerNotesText}}<pre>{{playerNotesText}}</pre>{{/if}}</article>{{else}}<div class="ds-inline-empty">No processed months yet.</div>{{/each}}</section>
          </section>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if (eq activeTab "rules")}}
          <section class="ds-pane">
            <section class="ds-section"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2>Settlement Hierarchy</h2><span>Building Tier 1-5 follows Hamlet-Metropolis</span></div><div class="ds-rules-tier-grid">{{#each tierRules}}<article><span>{{name}}</span><h3>{{baseIncomePerFreePop}} Crown</h3><p>per Free POP each month</p><small>{{minPopulationDisplay}} POP required / {{openSlots}} open / {{maxSlots}} maximum slots</small><small>{{promotionCostDisplay}} Crown / {{promotionMaterialsDisplay}} Materials / {{promotionCpDisplay}} CP to develop</small></article>{{/each}}</div></section>
            <section class="ds-rules-grid">
              <article class="ds-section ds-rule-chapter"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i> POP and Income</h2></div><p>One POP represents roughly ten residents. An operating building automatically reserves its full required POP. If enough POP is unavailable it waits, produces nothing, and pays half upkeep. A halted building also pays half upkeep. Soldiers use Manpower, not civilian POP.</p><p><strong>Monthly Crown:</strong> Free POP x settlement tier income, plus Commerce and hybrid-building income, then Public Order and policy modifiers, minus building and army upkeep.</p><dl class="ds-rule-list"><div><dt>Current tier income</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.baseIncomePerFreePop}} / Free POP</dd></div><div><dt>Current base income</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.baseIncome}}</dd></div><div><dt>Building upkeep discount</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.buildingUpkeepDiscount}}</dd></div></dl></article>
              <article class="ds-section ds-rule-chapter"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2><i class="fa-solid fa-wheat-awn"></i> Food and Materials</h2></div><p>Food is a monthly flow, not stored currency. Every POP consumes {{rules.economy.foodPerPop}} Food and regiments add their listed consumption. Grain branches maximize Food. Pastoral branches trade some Food for Crown, Growth, and recruitment savings.</p><p>Stone branches maximize Materials and Construction CP. Foundry branches trade some Materials for Crown and military discounts. Commerce specializes in Crown; Civic specializes in Order, Growth, event control, and mitigation.</p><dl class="ds-rule-list"><div><dt>Food produced / consumed</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.foodProduction}} / {{selected.summary.foodConsumption}}</dd></div><div><dt>Food balance</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.foodBalance}}</dd></div><div><dt>Materials balance</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.materialsBalance}}</dd></div></dl></article>
              <article class="ds-section ds-rule-chapter"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2><i class="fa-solid fa-seedling"></i> Growth and Food Security</h2></div><p>Food Security uses this exact production-to-consumption coverage: Starvation below 50% gives -3% Growth; Severe Shortage 50-74% gives -2%; Shortage 75-99% gives -1%; Sustained 100-124% gives 0%; Well Fed 125-149% gives +0.5%; Plentiful 150-199% gives +1%; Abundant 200% or more gives +1.5%.</p><p>Population Growth Pressure begins at {{rules.growth.populationPressureStart}} POP, applies -{{rules.growth.populationPressurePerDoubling}}% per doubling, and caps at -{{rules.growth.populationPressureCap}}%. More population therefore requires continued Food and Civic investment.</p><dl class="ds-rule-list"><div><dt>Food Security</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.foodSecurity}} / {{selected.summary.foodCoverage}}</dd></div><div><dt>Security effects</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.foodSecurityGrowth}} / {{selected.summary.foodSecurityEventRoll}}</dd></div><div><dt>Population Pressure</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.populationPressure}}</dd></div></dl></article>
              <article class="ds-section ds-rule-chapter"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2><i class="fa-solid fa-hammer"></i> Construction</h2></div><p>Free POP creates CP each month. Crown and Materials are paid when a project enters the queue; CP then advances it over later months. Food is never a construction currency.</p><p>Each district holds one branch. Development replaces the building in that slot with one of its direct children. Branches split at the same tier and cannot jump across parents.</p><dl class="ds-rule-list"><div><dt>CP per Free POP</dt><dd>{{rules.construction.cpPerFreePop}}</dd></div><div><dt>Current CP</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.cpThisMonth}}</dd></div><div><dt>Queue overflow</dt><dd>{{#if rules.construction.overflowToNextProject}}Enabled{{else}}Disabled{{/if}}</dd></div></dl></article>
              <article class="ds-section ds-rule-chapter"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2><i class="fa-solid fa-khanda"></i> Armies and Manpower</h2></div><p>Force Capacity equals Total POP x {{rules.military.manpowerRate}}%, so 309 POP supports at most 309 active and queued soldiers. Manpower Reserve is spent by recruitment and replenishment and recovers {{rules.military.manpowerRecoveryRate}}% of its cap each processed month.</p><p>All raised units pay one upkeep equal to {{rules.military.upkeepPercent}}% of recruit price per month. Recruitment Capacity is pooled from operating military buildings and limits new training that month. Replenishment costs {{rules.economy.replenishmentCostPercent}}% of recruit price, uses Manpower, requires no building, and consumes no Recruitment Capacity.</p><dl class="ds-rule-list"><div><dt>Current Reserve</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.manpowerReserve}} / {{selected.summary.manpowerCap}}</dd></div><div><dt>Next Recovery</dt><dd>+{{selected.summary.manpowerRecovery}}</dd></div><div><dt>Recruitment Capacity</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.recruitmentCapacity}} / month</dd></div></dl></article>
              <article class="ds-section ds-rule-chapter"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2><i class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced"></i> Public Order, Garrisons, and Events</h2></div><p>Public Order bands have exact effects: Unrest 0-24 gives -50% Crown and -1% Growth; Unstable 25-49 gives -25% Crown and -0.5% Growth; Stable 50-74 gives no modifier; Content 75-89 gives +10% Crown and +0.25% Growth; Prosperous 90-100 gives +20% Crown and +0.5% Growth. Population Order Pressure begins at {{rules.order.populationPressureStart}} POP, adds -{{rules.order.populationPressurePerDoubling}} Order per doubling, and caps at -{{rules.order.populationPressureCap}}.</p><p>Defense buildings create the listed free auto-garrison and explicit Siege Defense percentage. Auto-garrison pays no army upkeep and does not consume Manpower. Siege Defense reduces harmful defense-tagged event modifiers. Events never grant flat resources automatically; the GM approves percentage effects or keeps them narrative-only.</p><dl class="ds-rule-list"><div><dt>Current Order</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.publicOrder}} / {{selected.summary.publicOrderBand}}</dd></div><div><dt>Order Effects</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.publicOrderGrowth}} / {{selected.summary.publicOrderIncome}}</dd></div><div><dt>Population Order Pressure</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.publicOrderPressure}}</dd></div><div><dt>Auto Garrison</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.autoGarrisonSummary}} / {{selected.summary.autoGarrisonPower}} Power</dd></div><div><dt>Siege Defense</dt><dd>{{selected.summary.siegeDefense}}</dd></div></dl></article>
              <article class="ds-section ds-rule-chapter"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2><i class="fa-solid fa-scroll"></i> Policies</h2></div><p>Each settlement has one active policy. Stronger policies unlock with settlement tier and exchange one advantage for a visible economic, Food, order, or growth cost.</p><div class="ds-policy-list">{{#each policies}}<div><strong>{{name}}</strong><span>{{tierLabel}}</span><p>{{description}}</p></div>{{/each}}</div></article>
            </section>
            {{#if isGM}}
              <section class="ds-section"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2>Edit World Rules</h2></div><div class="ds-rules-editor-grid">
                <form class="ds-panel" data-action-form="updateRulesEconomy"><div class="ds-panel-heading"><h2>Economy</h2><button type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i></button></div><label><span>Income Multiplier</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="incomeMultiplier" value="{{rules.economy.incomeMultiplier}}"></label><label><span>Hired CP Cost</span><input type="number" name="constructionHireCostPerCp" value="{{rules.economy.constructionHireCostPerCp}}"></label><label><span>Food / POP</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="foodPerPop" value="{{rules.economy.foodPerPop}}"></label><label><span>Subsistence Food / Free POP</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="subsistenceFoodPerFreePop" value="{{rules.economy.subsistenceFoodPerFreePop}}"></label><label><span>Replenishment Cost %</span><input type="number" name="replenishmentCostPercent" value="{{rules.economy.replenishmentCostPercent}}"></label><label><span>Recruit Discount Cap %</span><input type="number" name="recruitmentDiscountCap" value="{{rules.economy.recruitmentDiscountCap}}"></label><label><span>Upkeep Discount Cap %</span><input type="number" name="upkeepDiscountCap" value="{{rules.economy.upkeepDiscountCap}}"></label></form>
                <form class="ds-panel" data-action-form="updateRulesConstruction"><div class="ds-panel-heading"><h2>Construction</h2><button type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i></button></div><label><span>CP / Free POP</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="cpPerFreePop" value="{{rules.construction.cpPerFreePop}}"></label><label><span>Cancellation Refund %</span><input type="number" name="cancellationRefundPercent" value="{{rules.construction.cancellationRefundPercent}}"></label><label><span>Turn Snapshots</span><input type="number" name="snapshotLimit" value="{{rules.construction.snapshotLimit}}" min="1" max="20"></label><label class="ds-toggle"><input type="checkbox" name="overflowToNextProject" data-bool {{#if rules.construction.overflowToNextProject}}checked{{/if}}><span>Overflow to next project</span></label></form>
                <form class="ds-panel" data-action-form="updateRulesMilitary"><div class="ds-panel-heading"><h2>Military</h2><button type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i></button></div><label><span>Force Capacity / POP %</span><input type="number" name="manpowerRate" value="{{rules.military.manpowerRate}}"></label><label><span>Reserve Recovery / Month %</span><input type="number" name="manpowerRecoveryRate" value="{{rules.military.manpowerRecoveryRate}}" min="0" max="100"></label><label><span>Unit Upkeep / Recruit Cost %</span><input type="number" step="0.1" name="upkeepPercent" value="{{rules.military.upkeepPercent}}" min="0" max="100"></label></form>
                <form class="ds-panel" data-action-form="updateRulesGrowth"><div class="ds-panel-heading"><h2>Growth and Order Pressure</h2><button type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i></button></div><label><span>Minimum Monthly %</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="minimumRate" value="{{rules.growth.minimumRate}}"></label><label><span>Maximum Monthly %</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="maximumRate" value="{{rules.growth.maximumRate}}"></label><label><span>Growth Pressure Starts at POP</span><input type="number" name="populationPressureStart" value="{{rules.growth.populationPressureStart}}" min="1"></label><label><span>Growth Pressure / Doubling %</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="populationPressurePerDoubling" value="{{rules.growth.populationPressurePerDoubling}}" min="0"></label><label><span>Growth Pressure Cap %</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="populationPressureCap" value="{{rules.growth.populationPressureCap}}" min="0"></label><label><span>Order Pressure Starts at POP</span><input type="number" name="orderPressureStart" value="{{rules.order.populationPressureStart}}" min="1"></label><label><span>Order Loss / Doubling</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="orderPressurePerDoubling" value="{{rules.order.populationPressurePerDoubling}}" min="0"></label><label><span>Order Pressure Cap</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="orderPressureCap" value="{{rules.order.populationPressureCap}}" min="0"></label></form>
                <form class="ds-panel" data-action-form="updateRulesEvents"><div class="ds-panel-heading"><h2>Month Events</h2><button type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i></button></div><p>Food Security and Public Order already provide their exact roll modifiers.</p><label class="ds-toggle"><input type="checkbox" name="enabled" data-bool {{#if rules.events.enabled}}checked{{/if}}><span>Roll 1d100 each month</span></label></form>
              </div></section>
              <section class="ds-section"><div class="ds-section-heading"><h2>Edit Settlement Tiers</h2></div><div class="ds-tier-editor-list">{{#each tierRules}}<form data-action-form="updateRuleTier"><input type="hidden" name="tierId" value="{{id}}"><label><span>Name</span><input name="name" value="{{name}}"></label><label><span>Core Building</span><input name="coreName" value="{{coreName}}"></label><label><span>Base Income / Free POP</span><input type="number" name="baseIncomePerFreePop" value="{{baseIncomePerFreePop}}"></label><label><span>Minimum POP</span><input type="number" name="minPopulation" value="{{minPopulation}}"></label><label><span>Open Slots</span><input type="number" name="openSlots" value="{{openSlots}}"></label><label><span>Maximum Slots</span><input type="number" name="maxSlots" value="{{maxSlots}}"></label><label><span>Promotion Crown</span><input type="number" name="promotionCost" value="{{promotionCost}}"></label><label><span>Promotion Materials</span><input type="number" name="promotionMaterials" value="{{promotionMaterials}}"></label><label><span>Promotion CP</span><input type="number" name="promotionCp" value="{{promotionCp}}"></label><label><span>Slot Unlock Crown</span><input type="number" name="slotUnlockCost" value="{{slotUnlockCost}}"></label><label><span>Active Projects</span><input type="number" name="activeProjects" value="{{activeProjects}}" min="1" max="5"></label><button type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i></button></form>{{/each}}</div></section>
            {{/if}}
          </section>
        {{/if}}

        {{#if (eq activeTab "catalog")}}
          <section class="ds-pane">
            <section class="ds-section">
              <div class="ds-section-heading"><div><h2>Content Library</h2><p>Five-tier building families, unit templates, and d100 events</p></div><div class="ds-section-actions"><div class="ds-segmented"><button type="button" data-catalog-kind="buildings" class="{{#if catalogBuildingsActive}}active{{/if}}"><i class="fa-solid fa-building"></i> Buildings</button><button type="button" data-catalog-kind="units" class="{{#if catalogUnitsActive}}active{{/if}}"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> Units</button><button type="button" data-catalog-kind="events" class="{{#if catalogEventsActive}}active{{/if}}"><i class="fa-solid fa-dice-d20"></i> Events</button></div><input type="search" data-search-catalog value="{{catalogSearch}}" placeholder="Search library">{{#if catalogBuildingsActive}}<button type="button" class="ds-primary" data-click-action="addCatalogBuilding" data-building-kind="economic"><i class="fa-solid fa-coins"></i><span>Economic</span></button><button type="button" class="ds-primary" data-click-action="addCatalogBuilding" data-building-kind="military"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i><span>Military</span></button><button type="button" class="ds-primary" data-click-action="addCatalogBuilding" data-building-kind="landmark"><i class="fa-solid fa-crown"></i><span>Landmark</span></button>{{else if catalogUnitsActive}}<button type="button" class="ds-primary" data-click-action="addCatalogUnit"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i><span>Unit</span></button>{{else}}<button type="button" class="ds-primary" data-click-action="addCatalogEvent"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i><span>Event</span></button>{{/if}}</div></div>
              {{#if catalogBuildingsActive}}
                <div class="ds-library-tree-grid">
                  {{#each catalogBuildingTrees}}
                    <article class="ds-branch-tree {{className}}"><header><i class="fa-solid {{icon}}"></i><strong>{{label}}</strong></header><div class="ds-branch-levels">{{#each levels}}<div class="ds-branch-level"><span class="ds-tier-marker">{{tierLabel}}</span><div class="ds-branch-level-nodes" style="--tree-columns: {{columnCount}};">{{#each nodes}}<div class="ds-tree-node" tabindex="0" style="{{treeStyle}}">{{#if hasImage}}<img src="{{imageUrl}}" alt="{{name}}">{{else}}<i class="fa-solid {{categoryIcon}}"></i>{{/if}}<strong>{{name}}</strong><small>{{parentNames}}</small><div class="ds-node-tooltip"><h4>{{name}}</h4><p>{{description}}</p><span class="ds-effect-badges">{{#each effectBadges}}<em class="{{kind}}"><i class="fa-solid {{icon}}"></i>{{label}}</em>{{/each}}</span><small>{{settlementTierLabel}} / {{crownCost}} Crown / {{materialCost}} Materials / {{cpCost}} CP</small></div></div>{{/each}}</div></div>{{/each}}</div></article>
                  {{/each}}
                </div>
                <div class="ds-editor-list">
                  {{#each catalogBuildingTrees}}
                    <details class="ds-library-branch {{className}}"><summary><i class="fa-solid {{icon}}"></i><strong>{{label}}</strong><span>{{nodes.length}} nodes</span><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i></summary><div class="ds-library-branch-body">
                    {{#each nodes}}
                    <details class="ds-record-card {{branchClass}}">
                      <summary><div class="ds-summary-image">{{#if hasImage}}<img src="{{imageUrl}}" alt="{{name}}">{{else}}<i class="fa-solid {{categoryIcon}}"></i>{{/if}}</div><div><h3>{{name}}{{#if special}} <i class="fa-solid fa-star ds-special-mark"></i>{{/if}}</h3><p>{{branchLabel}} / {{nodeTierLabel}}</p><small>{{description}}</small><span class="ds-effect-badges">{{#each effectBadges}}<em class="{{kind}}"><i class="fa-solid {{icon}}"></i>{{label}}</em>{{/each}}</span></div><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i></summary>
                      <form class="ds-editor-body" data-action-form="updateCatalogBuilding">
                        <input type="hidden" name="catalogId" value="{{id}}">
                        <div class="ds-form-grid">
                          <label><span>Name</span><input name="name" value="{{name}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Category</span><select name="category">{{#each categoryOptions}}<option value="{{value}}" {{#if selected}}selected{{/if}}>{{label}}</option>{{/each}}</select></label>
                           <label><span>Family ID</span><input name="chainId" value="{{chainId}}"></label>
                           <label><span>Branch</span><select name="branch">{{#each branchOptions}}<option value="{{id}}" {{#if selected}}selected{{/if}}>{{label}}</option>{{/each}}</select></label>
                          <label><span>Tier (1-5, 0 Landmark)</span><input type="number" name="nodeTier" value="{{nodeTier}}" min="0" max="5"></label>
                          <label class="ds-full"><span>Parent Node IDs</span><input name="parentIds" value="{{parentIdsText}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Settlement Tier</span><input value="{{settlementTierLabel}}" disabled></label>
                          <label><span>Terrain</span><input name="terrain" value="{{terrain}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Crown Cost</span><input type="number" name="crownCost" value="{{crownCost}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Materials Cost</span><input type="number" name="materialCost" value="{{materialCost}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>CP Cost</span><input type="number" name="cpCost" value="{{cpCost}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Workers</span><input type="number" name="workers" value="{{workers}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Crown / Worker</span><input type="number" name="rate" value="{{rate}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Flat Crown</span><input type="number" name="flatOutput" value="{{flatOutput}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Crown Upkeep</span><input type="number" name="buildingUpkeep" value="{{buildingUpkeep}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Food Output</span><input type="number" name="foodOutput" value="{{foodOutput}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Materials Output</span><input type="number" name="materialsOutput" value="{{materialsOutput}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Food Upkeep</span><input type="number" name="foodUpkeep" value="{{foodUpkeep}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Materials Upkeep</span><input type="number" name="materialsUpkeep" value="{{materialsUpkeep}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Public Order</span><input type="number" name="publicOrder" value="{{publicOrder}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Siege Defense %</span><input type="number" name="siegeDefensePercent" value="{{siegeDefensePercent}}" min="0" max="100"></label>
                          <label class="ds-full"><span>Free Garrison (unit-id:count)</span><input name="garrisonUnits" value="{{garrisonUnitsText}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Event Roll Bonus</span><input type="number" name="eventRollBonus" value="{{eventRollBonus}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Construction CP</span><input type="number" name="constructionBonus" value="{{constructionBonus}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Recruit / Month</span><input type="number" name="recruitPerLevel" value="{{recruitPerLevel}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Recruit Discount %</span><input type="number" name="recruitmentDiscount" value="{{recruitmentDiscount}}" min="0" max="100"></label>
                          <label><span>Upkeep Discount %</span><input type="number" name="upkeepDiscount" value="{{upkeepDiscount}}" min="0" max="100"></label>
                          <label><span>Building Upkeep Discount %</span><input type="number" name="buildingUpkeepDiscount" value="{{buildingUpkeepDiscount}}" min="0" max="100"></label>
                          <label><span>Growth %</span><input type="number" step="0.01" name="growth" value="{{growth}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Slot Use</span><input type="number" name="slotUse" value="{{slotUse}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label><span>Economic Bonus Slots</span><input type="number" name="bonusEconomicSlots" value="{{bonusEconomicSlots}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Military Bonus Slots</span><input type="number" name="bonusMilitarySlots" value="{{bonusMilitarySlots}}"></label>
                          <label><span>Max per Settlement</span><input type="number" name="maxPerSettlement" value="{{maxPerSettlement}}" min="0"></label>
                          <label class="ds-full"><span>Event Mitigation Tags</span><input name="mitigationTags" value="{{mitigationTagsText}}"></label>
                           <label class="ds-full"><span>Image</span><div class="ds-input-action"><input name="imageUrl" value="{{imageUrl}}"><button type="button" data-file-picker="[name='imageUrl']"><i class="fa-solid fa-image"></i></button></div></label>
                           <label class="ds-full"><span>Description</span><textarea name="description" rows="2">{{description}}</textarea></label>
                          <label class="ds-toggle"><input type="checkbox" name="enabled" data-bool {{enabledChecked}}><span>Enabled</span></label>
                          <label class="ds-toggle"><input type="checkbox" name="special" data-bool {{specialChecked}}><span>Special</span></label>
                          <label class="ds-toggle"><input type="checkbox" name="landmark" data-bool {{landmarkChecked}}><span>Tierless Landmark</span></label>
                          <label class="ds-toggle"><input type="checkbox" name="gmOnly" data-bool {{gmOnlyChecked}}><span>GM Only</span></label>
                          <label class="ds-toggle"><input type="checkbox" name="uniqueChain" data-bool {{uniqueChainChecked}}><span>One family per settlement</span></label>
                          <label class="ds-toggle"><input type="checkbox" name="canRecruit" data-bool {{canRecruitChecked}}><span>Can Recruit Units</span></label>
                          <fieldset class="ds-check-grid ds-full"><legend>Recruitable Units</legend><input type="hidden" name="recruitableUnitIds" value="">{{#each unitOptions}}<label><input type="checkbox" name="recruitableUnitIds" value="{{id}}" {{#if checked}}checked{{/if}}> {{name}}</label>{{/each}}</fieldset>
                          <label class="ds-full"><span>Notes</span><textarea name="notes" rows="2">{{notes}}</textarea></label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ds-record-actions"><button type="submit"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i><span>Save Node</span></button><button type="button" data-click-action="applyCatalogBuilding" data-catalog-id="{{id}}" data-confirm="Apply this template to every existing instance?"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrows-rotate"></i><span>Apply Existing</span></button>{{#unless isBuiltIn}}<button type="button" class="ds-danger" data-click-action="deleteCatalogBuilding" data-catalog-id="{{id}}" data-confirm="Delete this unused building node?"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash"></i></button>{{/unless}}</div>
                      </form>
                     </details>
                   {{/each}}
                   </div></details>
                  {{/each}}
                </div>
              {{else if catalogUnitsActive}}
                <div class="ds-editor-list">
                  {{#each catalogUnits}}
                    <details class="ds-record-card">
